      "text": "<p>Vas <code>img</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>smaller-image</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('img').classList.contains('smaller-image'));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Vas <code>img</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>thick-green-border</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('img').classList.contains('thick-green-border'));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Vasa slika treba da ima okvir sirine <code>10px</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "// Note: to any future maintainers, the read width of the border is dependent on \n// the zoom. For example we cannot match 10px exactly because if a campers set the zoom to 110% \n// it will be read as 9~px. \nconst image = document.querySelector('img'); \nconst imageBorderTopWidth = window.getComputedStyle(image)[\"border-top-width\"]; \nconst widthNumber = parseInt(imageBorderTopWidth);\nassert.isAtLeast(widthNumber, 8);\nassert.isAtMost(widthNumber, 12);"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Vasa slika treba da ima stil okvira <code>solid</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const image = document.querySelector('img'); \nconst borderRightStyle = window.getComputedStyle(image)[\"border-right-style\"]; \nassert.strictEqual(borderRightStyle, 'solid');"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Okvir oko vaseg <code>img</code> elementa treba da bude zelene boje.</p>",
      "testString": "const image = document.querySelector('img'); \nconst borderLeftColor = window.getComputedStyle(image)[\"border-left-color\"]; \nassert.strictEqual(borderLeftColor, 'rgb(0, 128, 0)');"
    }
  ],
  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>CSS okviri imaju svojstva kao sto su <code>style</code>, <code>color</code> i <code>width</code>.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako bismo zeleli da napravimo crveni okvir od 5 piksela oko HTML elementa, mogli bismo koristiti ovu klasu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;style>\n  .thin-red-border {\n    border-color: red;\n    border-width: 5px;\n    border-style: solid;\n  }\n&#x3C;/style>\n</code></pre>\n</section>",
  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite klasu <code>thick-green-border</code>. Ova klasa treba da doda zeleni, puni okvir sirine 10px oko HTML elementa. Primenite ovu klasu na sliku macke.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da mozete koristiti vise klasa na jednom elementu pomocu <code>class</code> atributa, razdvajajuci nazive klasa razmacima. Na primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;img class=\"class1 class2\">\n</code></pre>\n</section>",
